[Student "S"]
{NORTH has 13 points but has no bid over 1\D. 
SOUTH can make a Takeout Double, so he does.

NORTH now cue-bids \D to show opening hand strength.

SOUTH shows his \H suit, NORTH doesn't like it. 
NORTH shows her \S suit, SOUTH doesn't like it. 
SOUTH shows his \C suit, NORTH likes it fine, but decides 3NT will be easier than 5\C.}

